/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4f00b65dc8f2dea4b645ac4083451db8a8a2df","tid":1478544,"uid":69040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T20:00:25.000Z","msg":"點解推唔到post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}